   After passing the TAXI screen you are faced with various options.

   POLICE STATION:



   In  the Police Station you can see which gangsters are  wanted  along 

   with their name and description.  On the wanted board you will see  a 

   picture of a gangster.  Click on this and you will get a close up  of 

   it displaying the gangsters name,  description,  and what he's wanted 

   for. Make a note of this info for later. Click button to exit.

   

   LOCAL BAR:



   If  a gangster is in town he will useally be seen in the  local  pub. 

   See SHOOTOUT. In the bar you can either leave by clicking on the door 

   or  go  and play pontoon by clicking on the small icon at  the  right 

   hand side of the screen.



   PONTOON:



   You can make more money by playing Pontoon,  normal rules apply,  you 

   and  the dealer must get as close to a score of 21 as  possible.  You 

   can twist,  stick,  or raise the bet by moving the mouse pointer over 

   the  options and clicking on them when their  highlighted.  Click  on 

   EXIT to leave and go back to the bar.

 

   PAPERSTAND:



   The  big boss has sent his henchmen after you and  their  whereabouts 

   can  be found by reading the local paper.  Click on the paperboy  and 

   ask him for the paper,  bearing in mind that each copy costs a pound. 

   The paper will explain where the henchmen were last seen.

   When a gangster has commited a crime his face will appear here and his

   details in the police station on a wanted poster.


   GUNSTORE:



   This option leaves you stood outside the gunstore.  Note that if  the 

   henchmen  are in town the they will appear here and  shoot  you.

   Click on the door to enter the gunstore or on the road to leave.



   Once you're in the store you can buy guns and ammo by clicking on the 

   icons on the shelves, note you can only buy rifles, magnums, bullets, 

   and grenades.  Your money appears in the bottom left and corner which 

   decreased  by  the price of the item bought.  Press  the  left  mouse 

   button to buy the items and right button to leave.



   There  is also an hidden Food Store which works the same as  the  Gun 

   Store. The food is truffles, hamburgers, pop, and fags!!!!



   BIG BOSS:



   You can only go here if you have all twelve pieces of map.



   There are other places you can go to as well,  note that if you click 

   on  the drawing of a character you can have a chat  with  them.  Some 

   give you information while some just talk silly.  Move the mouse over 

   the  text  to say something to that character and click on  the  text 

   see their answer.



   SHOOTOUT:



   As mentioned before, when you enter the pub there will sometimes be a 

   gangster in there.  If one is found then you will be given the option 

   to  challenge him.  If you decide to do so you will be asked who  you 

   think he is.  Get the name wrong and you will be arrested for  murder 

   should  you  shoot  him.   The  message  before  will  give  you  his 

   description and you name him according to his description.  So if you

   think  Sean Silly is the man who limps with his left leg then  select 

   his name.

 

   Once the name is selected you go to the back of the pub to face  each 

   other.  Wait till he draws then press either the left mouse button to 

   shoot him if you have bullets or right mouse button to blow him up if 

   you have grenades........you only get one chance.  After shooting him 

   you take him to the police who will either reward you or throw you in 

   jail depending on if you got his name right.



